## Virtual Tools

Compose native tools via a declarative pipeline DSL:

```yaml
virtualTools:
  - name: MyVirtualTool
    description: Chain multiple native tools together
    inputSchema:
      type: object
      properties:
        appId: { type: string }
      required: [appId]
    pipeline:
      - id: getApp
        kind: call
        spec: { tool: GetApplication, args: { applicationId: "$input.appId" } }
      - id: appName
        kind: jq
        spec: { from: "$getApp", expr: .name }
      - id: done
        kind: return
        spec: { from: "$appName" }
```

Pipeline kinds: `call`, `jq`, `foreach`, `emit`, `return`.

## Agent Integration

### OpenCode

- `~/.config/opencode/opencode.json`:

```json
{
  "mcp": {
    "{{ .BinaryName }}": {
      "type": "local",
      "command": ["bash", "-c", "/path/to/{{ .BinaryName }}"],
      "args": ["--transport", "stdio"],
      "env": {
        "MCP__UPSTREAM__ENDPOINT": "https://api.example.com",
        "MCP__AUTH__BACKEND__STATIC__BEARER_TOKEN": "your-token",
        "MCP__AUTH__BACKEND__STATIC__BEARER_TOKEN_FILE": "/path/to/fallback/.credentials"
      },
      "enabled": true
    }
  }
}
```

### Claude Code

- `~/.claude.json`:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "{{ .BinaryName }}": {
      "command": "/path/to/{{ .BinaryName }}",
      "args": ["--transport", "stdio"],
      "env": {
        "MCP__UPSTREAM__ENDPOINT": "https://api.example.com",
        "MCP__AUTH__BACKEND__STATIC__BEARER_TOKEN": "your-token",
        "MCP__AUTH__BACKEND__STATIC__BEARER_TOKEN_FILE": "/path/to/fallback/.credentials"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

